GANGDONG POLICE STATION

37
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:53,560
Sorry, guys.
It was just a misunderstanding.

38
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,000
It was a total misunderstanding.

39
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,440
Did you use to train?

40
