47
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,160
I need Feifei to treat my injury.

48
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,880
Come on.

49
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,040
Let's go home.

50
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,680
Let's go.

51
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,080
Are you okay?

52
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,560
I'm fine if you're fine.

53
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,320
Ling Yizhou.

54
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:42,200
There's a question
I've been meaning to ask you.

55
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,200
Ask away.

56
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,600
Why me?

57
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,240
In Feifei's words,

58
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:50,440
you're handsome, come from a good family
and you're devoted.

59
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,600
You must be what a lot of women find
to be the perfect husband.

60
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,280
Really?

61
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:59,400
Mumu, do you think
I am the perfect husband?

62
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,040
You nearly changed the subject
on me again.

63
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,440
You haven't answered me yet.

64
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,120
Okay.

65
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,040
So you're asking me

66
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,800
why I chose you instead of somebody else?

67
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:16,920
I just think that in most people's eyes,

68
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,960
I'm not the best choice for you.

69
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,440
On an emotional level,

70
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:23,160
I won't cling to you like a helpless bird.

71
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,440
On a professional level,

72
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,640
I'm not even remotely qualified
to join forces with you.

73
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,800
Our meeting was purely by accident.

74
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,640
You could have refused to help me.

75
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:34,240
Yet, you chose to use
an engagement contract

76
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:36,120
to tighten the ties between us.

77
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,240
After that,

78
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,880
whether it was acting like a couple

79
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,720
or taking part in a reality show,

80
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,200
you gave your full cooperation.

81
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:46,480
You could have terminated the contract,
but you chose to continue it.

82
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:49,040
From a businessman's perspective,

83
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:52,520
I can't see any benefit
you might gain from this.

84
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:53,960
How amazing.

85
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:57,240
You're gaining strong business acumen.

86
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,200
You're right.

87
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:02,560
But what you've seen
is just the tip of the iceberg.

88
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,720
Let me put it this way.

89
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:09,560
If you say that our engagement contract
was a scheme,

90
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,960
I wouldn't deny it.

91
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,720
Come on. Over here.

92
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,000
Why did you take me away? What about them?

93
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:21,360
You're worried about them?

94
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,480
Boss is with Ms. Xia.

95
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,800
They will be fine.

96
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,680
I'm worried about Xia Lin.

97
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,160
Worried about Ms. Xia?

98
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:32,000
Didn't you see
how Boss protected her today?

99
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,640
Do you think she would be in danger?

100
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,320
You should worry about me instead.

101
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,120
I'm in pain.

102
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,600
How could you be injured?

103
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,160
You didn't even fight.

104
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:45,000
I was hugging you the entire afternoon.

105
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,640
You were just taking advantage of me.

106
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:54,400
I want every day to be like today.

107
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,760
I want to protect you.

108
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,280
Even if I don't get physical.

109
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,880
As for why I don't want
to terminate the contract,

110
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,680
it's because of my ultimate goal

111
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,360
which is what you're asking about.

112
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:12,560
What do I stand to gain
from this agreement?

113
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:18,240
The greatest value in this agreement
is making you fall for me.

114
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:22,640
The submerged part of the iceberg
that you don't see...

115
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,560
is that I like you.

116
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,840
I want to be with you.

117
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,920
If that is your objective,

118
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:38,920
then don't I hold all the power?

119
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,200
Ms. Xia.

120
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:44,840
The duration of the contract
is explicitly defined in the agreement.

121
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:45,880
All right.

122
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:49,800
Then I unilaterally declare
the engagement contract terminated.

123
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,360
I should warn you.

124
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:53,520
A unilateral termination is considered
a breach of contract.

125
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,400
You will have to pay a penalty.

126
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,840
Mr. Ling, that's a miscalculation
on your part.

127
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:01,280
Do you dare to come with me?

128
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:04,040
I don't see why not.

129
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,000
Where are we going?

130
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,640
You'll see.

131
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,120
Feifei.

132
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,160
Doesn't it look like
we're in matching couples outfits?

133
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,000
In that case,

134
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:24,800
