181
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,200
We haven't slept all night.

182
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,800
Time for bed?

183
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,200
Yes, we need to sleep.

184
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,280
But before that,

185
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,680
